data.description: This captivating 3-bed, 2-bath, 2095 sqft haven awaits immediate occupancy, embodying the perfect blend of comfort and style. Meticulously tailored for modern living, it boasts freshly painted walls and gleaming linoleum floors creating a warm, sophisticated ambiance. Abundant natural light bathes every corner, setting the stage for cherished moments. New light fixtures add exquisite touches to tranquil bedrooms, including the master suite with a private en-suite—a rejuvenating haven. Step outside to enjoy morning coffee on the back patio, surrounded by lush greenery that extends your personal sanctuary. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream with new appliances and ample storage. An attached 2-car garage with epoxy floors adds convenience and style. Located in the prestigious Wylie Top Independent School District. Just beyond your doorstep lies Wylie's vibrant community, granting effortless access to shopping, dining, and amenities.
